Package com.flipkart.client

Class SlotActivityMenu

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.client.SlotActivityMenu
public class SlotActivityMenu extends Object
Represents the slot activity menu in the FlipFit system. This class provides functionalities for managing gym slots, including adding, booking, and canceling slots.
Author:
shivam
